\c 57
\s Rugare rwomoyo pakati penjodzi
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weAritasheti. Pisarema raDhavhidhi, rwiyo rweMikitami; panguva yaakatiza Sauro pabako.
\p
\v 1 . Ndinzwirei tsitsi, Mwari, ndinzwirei tsitsi; Nokuti mweya wangu unotizira kwamuri; Zvirokwazvo, ndichatizira kumumvuri wamapapiro enyu, Kusvikira njodzi dzapfuura.
\v 2 Ndichadanidzira kuna Mwari Wokumusorosoro; Kuna Mwari anondiitira zvose.
\v 3 Achatuma mubatsiri ari kudenga, andiponese, Kana iye, anovavarira kundimedza, achindishora; Mwari achatuma tsitsi dzake nezvokwadi yake.
\v 4 Mweya wangu uri pakati peshumba; Ndinovata pasi pakati pavanopfuta somoto, Ivo vanakomana vavanhu, vana meno anenge mapfumo nemiseve, Uye rurimi rwavo munondo unopinza.
\v 5 Imwi mukudzwe Mwari, pamusoro pokudenga-denga; Kurumbidzwa kwenyu ngakuve kumusoro kwapasi pose.
\v 6 Vakateyira tsoka dzangu mumbure; Mweya wangu wakakotamiswa; Vakachera hunza pamberi pangu; Vawira mukati mayo vamene.
\v 7 moyo wangu wakasimba, Mwari, moyo wangu wakasimba; Ndichaimba, zvirokwazvo, ndichaimba nziyo dzokurumbidza.
\v 8 Muka iwe moyo wangu, muka iwe mutengeramwa nembira; Ini ndimene ndichamuka mangwanani.
\v 9 Ndichakuvongai, Ishe, pakati pendudzi dzavanhu; Ndichakuimbirai nziyo dzokurumbidza pakati pavahedheni.
\v 10 Nokuti ngoni dzenyu ihuru kusvikira kudenga-denga, Zvokwadi yenyu inosvikira kudenga rose.
\v 11 Imi mukudzwe Mwari, kumusoro kokudenga-denga; Kurumbidzwa kwenyu ngakuve kumusoro kwapasi pose.
